VALUES (
'
<span style="background-color: #9D0208; color: white; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; padding: 5px; display: inline-block; text-decoration: underline;">Release Summary - 09/09/2024 :</span>
<h4 style="margin-top: 0;">This release includes the following:</h4>
<ol>
    <li>Enhancements - 5
        <ul>
			<li>Created view to capture a few LC360 related fields requested by the analytics team</li>
			<li>External Integrations : Enhance the red zone data feed to capture 11 additional columns</li>
			<li>Added Metal 09/07 release related 14 new columns for Home & Condo</li>
			<li>Added term_no column to tpolicy and tquote tables. Backfill will be done during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
			<li>Added primary_auto_vehicle_sk column to tauto_driver and tquote_auto_driver.Backfill will be done during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
		</ul>
    </li>
    <li>Bug tickets - 33
        <ul>
			<li>Data Standardization : Fixed various limit fields (DeductibleWaiverLargeLossesLimit, HomeCyberProtectionCoverageLimit, HomeSystemsProtectionLimit, HomeCyberProtectionCoverageDeductible, HomeCyberProtectionCoverage and PersoanlLiabilityimit) for Home policies. Existing data updated only in Metal. EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
			<li>Data Standardization : Updated hurricane_deductible for RI Admitted policies.Existing data updated only in Metal. EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
			<li>Updated stored procdure to fetch wind_derived_deductible values from "manual" wind field columns when wind fields have "other" as a value.EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
			<li>Backfilled missing territory codes for a few policies based on prior policy terms.Existing data updated only in Metal. EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
			<li>Updated terminated producers status to disabled as per user request</li>
			<li>Updated broker_id for one agent as per user request</li>
			<li>Resolved 7 tickets associated with roofCoverageEndorsementRV; roofCoverageEndorsementWH; roofCoverageEndorsementAP fields by making them null</li>
			<li>Resolved 5 tickets associated with all the fixes we applied for IVANS data feed </li>
			<li>Resolved 3 tickets associated with county name fields. Existing data updated only in Metal. EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14 </li>
			<li>Resolved 2 tickets associated with moving policies from one customer accounts to other </li>
			<li>Resolved 2 tickets associated with updating the createddate in tnote table and loading data after 10th August</li>
			<li>Resolved 1 ticket associated with updating workercompensation_liability_parttime_employees_ct for 7 policies </li>
			<li>Resolved 1 ticket associated with updating barn_on_property_in and barn_value_amt for one policy </li>
			<li>Updated agreed_value_amt data type to capture accurate data.Existing data updated only in Metal. EDW will be backfilled during next EDW refresh on 09/14</li>
